OL,3,C'Dangerous' man jailed for 30 years
OL,4,Cover part in drug and gun supply chain
OL,6,FA "very dangerous" Darlington man has
OL,7,Fbeen jailed for 30 years for supplying
OL,8,Findustrial quantities of drugs and
OL,9,Ffirearms.
OL,11,FPeter Riley, 51, was arrested as part
OL,12,Fof Operation Venetic ` a national
OL,13,Fcrackdown on EncroChat - accused of
OL,14,Fconspiring to sell prohibited weapons,
OL,15,Fammunition, and Class A drugs across
OL,16,FDarlington and further afield.
OL,18,FEncroChat is one of the largest
OL,19,Fproviders of secure, encrypted
OL,20,Fcommunications, often used by
OL,21,Fcriminals.
