OL,4,Cover part in drug and gun supply chain
OL,6,FPolice gained access to messages from
OL,7,Fhis encrypted mobile phone which
OL,8,Fshowed Riley had been "heavily
OL,9,Finvolved" in the sourcing and onward
OL,10,Fsupply of firearms and large
OL,11,Fquantities of drugs.
OL,13,FHe had initially denied the offences,
OL,14,Fbut changed his plea to guilty before
OL,15,Fappearing at Teesside Crown Court on
OL,16,FMonday 26 February.
