OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Simon
OL,7,FTurner, Durham Constabulary, said:
OL,8,F"Riley is a very dangerous man who
OL,9,Fcared only about making vast amounts
OL,10,Fof money through the supply of illegal
OL,11,Ffirearms, ammunition, and drugs.
OL,13,F"He did not give a second thought to
OL,14,Fhow lethal these commodities were or
OL,15,Fthe devastating consequences they
OL,16,Fcould have on the communities of
OL,17,FCounty Durham and Darlington.
