OL,3,C'Dangerous' man jailed for 30 years
OL,4,Cover part in drug and gun supply chain
OL,6,F"By using encrypted messaging, Riley
OL,7,Fand his associates thought they were
OL,8,Funtouchable and above the law. But, by
OL,9,Fworking together with experts from the
OL,10,FNational Crime Agency, we were able to
OL,11,Fsystematically dismantle the network
OL,12,Fand show them this wasn't the case.
OL,14,F"I hope this sentence sends a strong
OL,15,Fmessage to others who are endangering
OL,16,Four communities by distributing
OL,17,Fillegal drugs and weapons that we will
OL,18,Ffind you, and we will bring you to
OL,19,Fjustice."
